Others have considered making predictions more explainable in the mental health domain. [explainability-deep-amini-2020] focused on leveraging a user-level attention mechanism for detecting signs of anorexia in social media profiles. Our method differs from theirs in that the explanations are the results of the analysis of the attention weights, while our approaches ground model predictions in a well-established clinical instrument.